<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>colculador de IMC</title>
    <link href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

    <!-- bootstrapp css -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>

<body id="body-container">
    <!--Header-start -->
    <header>
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1>Calculadora de Índice de Massa Corporal - IMC</h1>
        </div>

    </header>
    <!-- Header-and -->

    <div class="container">
        <div id="formulario" class="">
            <table class="table text-center">
                <thead class="table-dark">
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="col">IMC(kg/m<sup>2</sup>)</th>
                        <th scope="col">Resultado</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Menores que 18.5</td>
                        <td> Abaixo do Peso
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Entre 18.5 e 24.9</td>
                        <td>Peso Normal
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Entre 25 e 29.9 </td>
                        <td>Sobrepeso
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Entre 30 e 34.9 </td>
                        <td>Obesidade grau 1
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Entre 35 e 39.9</td>
                        <td>Obesidade grau 2
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Mais do que 40</td>
                        <td>Obesidade grau 3
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="bg-success bg-info text-center" id="info">
                <p>Para saber mais sobre IMC e sobre o resultado obtido no cálculo, <strong>clique no
                        botão azul</strong> para falar com
                    a assistente
                    virtual</p>
            </div>
            <form action="/" method="post">
                <div class="bg-success bg-gradient text-center">
                    <% if(imc){ %>
                        <p>
                            <strong>
                                <%=imc %>
                            </strong>
                        </p>
                        <% }%>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleInputPeso" class="form-label">Peso(kg)</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPeso" name="peso"
                        aria-describedby="emailHelp">
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="exampleInputAltura" class="form-label">Altura(m)</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="altura" id="exampleInputAltura">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Calcular</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div class="p-4 bg-dark bg-gradient" id="footer">
            <div>
                <p>make by</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/josedembo" target="_black" id="link">
                    <p> Jose Dembo</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <a href="https://github.com/demboProjects/Indice-de-massa-corporal-IMC" target="_black" id="link">
                <p>Projeto-GitHub</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
